    <div class="login-form-container">
        <div class="faq-container">
            
           
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        
			            <div class="faq">
			    <h3 class="faq-title">What is Book Vault?</h3>
			    <p class="faq-content">
			        Book Vault is a library management system designed to simplify the organization, tracking, and borrowing of books for libraries of all sizes.
			    </p>
			</div>
			<div class="faq">
			    <h3 class="faq-title">How can I register for Book Vault?</h3>
			    <p class="faq-content">
			        You can register by clicking on the "Sign Up" button on the login page and filling in your details. Once registered, you’ll receive an email confirmation.
			    </p>
			</div>
			<div class="faq">
			    <h3 class="faq-title">Is my data secure with Book Vault?</h3>
			    <p class="faq-content">
			        Yes, your data is securely encrypted and stored. We prioritize user privacy and adhere to strict data protection regulations.
			    </p>
			</div>
			<div class="faq">
			    <h3 class="faq-title">Can I access Book Vault on mobile devices?</h3>
			    <p class="faq-content">
			        Absolutely! Book Vault is designed to be fully responsive and works seamlessly on both desktop and mobile devices.
			    </p>
			</div>
			<div class="faq">
			    <h3 class="faq-title">How do I reset my password?</h3>
			    <p class="faq-content">
			        Click on the "Forgot Password" link on the login page, enter your registered email, and follow the instructions to reset your password.
			    </p>
			</div>
			<div class="faq">
			    <h3 class="faq-title">Does Book Vault support multiple languages?</h3>
			    <p class="faq-content">
			        Yes, Book Vault supports multiple languages to provide a better experience for users worldwide. You can select your preferred language in the settings.
			    </p>
			</div>
			<div class="faq">
			    <h3 class="faq-title">What types of reports can I generate?</h3>
			    <p class="faq-content">
			        Book Vault allows you to generate various reports, including borrowed books, overdue returns, and user activity logs, to monitor library operations effectively.
			    </p>
			</div>
			<div class="faq">
			    <h3 class="faq-title">Is there a limit to the number of books I can add?</h3>
			    <p class="faq-content">
			        No, there is no limit to the number of books you can add to Book Vault. It is designed to handle libraries of all sizes.
			    </p>
			</div>
			<div class="faq">
			    <h3 class="faq-title">How do I contact support?</h3>
			    <p class="faq-content">
			        You can contact our support team by visiting the "Help" section in your account or emailing us directly at support@bookvault.com.
			    </p>
			</div>
			<div class="faq">
			    <h3 class="faq-title">Can I customize Book Vault for my library?</h3>
			    <p class="faq-content">
			        Yes, Book Vault offers customization options to meet your library's specific needs, including branding and feature configuration.
			    </p>
			</div>

        </div>
    </div>

            
            

